
```````````````````Pipeline to build machine learning project step by step````````````````````````````
  
--Data Collection 
       collected the dataset for specific problem
--Data Cleaning
       clearning means check weather the dataset is noise value or prevent some
       error value ,check if there any null value . Understand the dataset properly
        
--Data analysis
       In this part we focus on dataset to which model is fit to the dataset
       for this reason we focus dataset deeply and undersatand the dataset and how it 
       behave  
--Data Visualualisation 
       To understand the dataset . We must visualize the dataset using some techonology
       we use matplotlib and seaborn for visualize the data

--data standardise 
     Pca(required) if high dimention 

--Data Processing 
    *text data into numerical
       - Categorical 
                 1.OneHotEnconder
                 2.labelEncoder
                   
       - numerical
               1.StandardScaler
               2.MinMaxScaler
                   
--Spliting the data
       - training (80) testing (20)

--Machine Learning model - 
         - KNN
         - Naive bayes
         - logistic regression
         - linear regression
         - decision tree
         - Random forest
         - Boosting algorithm
           ..................
           more.....

--Identify best parameters
         - hyperparameter tuning
             1.GridSearchCV
             2.RandomizedSearchCV
             
          # train acc and test acc are good, model is not overfitted #

--Evaluation 
         - accuracy score(balanced data)
         - f1_score [ generally everytime ]
         - precision [ Hihh risk situaion as 'healthcare' ]
         - recall [ special case use ]
         - confusion_metrics [ everytime ]
         - classification_report [ everytime ]

